{"tid":1912183,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"HKASA - 航空同業陣線 一個 真·屬於航空界嘅工會上線啦","createTime":"2020-03-06T01:16:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T10:46:37.000Z","uid":116474,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2368baddcb84395b1327b2e3eac3650b1836dc6e","tid":1912183,"uid":116474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T01:16:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔係由一個三唔識七 嘅廢老工聯會人無啦啦走出黎話代表航空界嘅工會</span></span> <br />\n                        <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁耐以黎都無一個正式幫航空界人士發聲嘅工會<br />\n到以家終於出現啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n工會簡介：<br />\n香港航空業界聯合工會是由八名熱愛香港的航空業員工所組成。香港機場一直聞名世界，是全球頂尖的機場之一，惟行內薪酬待遇、加班問題一直為人詬病。由於目前航空業還沒有一個可以代表到一眾員工的工會，所以我們希望透過成立公會以保障航空業員工的權益。<br />\n同業活動、各行打工仔聯合行動、會員優惠等詳情將陸續送上。<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">期待未來一年，和你飛，自由拍翼，彼此護航。</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yG97HBy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyG97HBy.jpg&h=97bedb4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n【#官方】最新消息發放，請密切留意：<br />\nTelegram 頻道 ▸ <a href=\"http://t.me/hkasalliance\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkasalliance&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcM%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=7e77b708\" data-auto-link targ